title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Equivalently, we can define a <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-0050.xml"
addr="jms-0050"
title="Duploid">duploid</fr:link> to be a <fr:link
type="local"
href="jms-004T.xml"
