href="jms-0050.xml"
addr="jms-0050"
title="Duploid">main definition</fr:link> implies our alternative definition, let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> be an object of the preduploid; because we are proving that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is <fr:em>merely equipped with</fr:em> both an <fr:link
